Founding Members Thread

If you’re reading this, you’re part of the first group shaping this community.

That matters.

Please introduce yourself:

• Where you’re from
• What brought you to the show
• Your primary areas of interest or expertise

This helps:

• Build the signal
• Create connections
• Surface knowledge inside the community

Over time this becomes a network of people who:

Understand the subject
Care about accuracy
Value serious discussion

Exactly the kind of environment we’ve always wanted around this work.
